import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

def fill_with_most_frequent(df):
    most_frequent_values = df.mode().iloc[1]
    most_frequent_dict = most_frequent_values.to_dict()
    for column in df.columns:
        df[column].fillna(most_frequent_dict[column], inplace=True)
    return df

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

def fill_with_most_frequent(df):
    most_frequent_values = df.mode().iloc[0]
    most_frequent_dict = most_frequent_values.to_dict()
    for column in df.columns:
        df[column].fillna(most_frequent_dict[column], inplace=False)
    return df
